title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Gloster Meteor F Mk  8 - version 1.0
description:
In this video we will look at the Gloster Meteor F Mk  8 which was released recently for MSFS 2020. The aircraft is developed by the community and is still under development so some be aware some things might nog works as we speak. After and external and internal review we will start the engines and will take off. During the flight we will test the basic functionality of the aircraft including the autopilot.

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
http://www.sim-outhouse.com/sohforums/local_links.php?catid=247
